<br>
If they fixed the haste cap, added BO5, and made frenzied burnout work, then at least the pet would start to scale up more (as I got better loot and exp, my pet would become more powerful, as meele's are getting more powerful) <p>Master Cydmab Promethean, Fury's Edge <BR>
